{"tid":946311,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"大學也應該分精英班和普通班","createTime":"2018-12-18T12:23:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T15:13:34.000Z","uid":198998,"like":11,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8d99e57c288a442d17c759bdab2399e0edfec60c","tid":946311,"uid":198998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"真的受不了那些要把簡單的事情重覆解釋數遍的lecturer<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該增設精英lecture和tutorial 上課時間減少一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826d92d0ac8815b65b84ceda90da683b38e40760","tid":946311,"uid":176802,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<br />\n唔撚識走堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb1e71e76d4eafe6b122eb6004a5446d3405a3d","tid":946311,"uid":198389,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"其實可愛&gt;&gt;靚仔<br />\n<br />\n第一 靚仔比可愛主觀 大家心目中嘅可愛都係差唔多 但靚仔就差好遠<br />\n<br />\n第二 靚仔好快睇厭 可愛日日睇都可以鍾意<br />\n<br />\n第三 靚仔容易走樣 講緊短短幾個月 可能肥少少已經keep唔到 可愛就唔同<br />\n<br />\n第四 靚仔好難同人close 可愛比較親民<br />\n<br />\n第五 靚仔比較多挑剔位 例如肌肉 高度 著衫 可愛真係有樣就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861d45942de954a741736957172c1786e0c3a07d","tid":946311,"uid":198998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"然後我全f要defer了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab75b517ffb1566aed317ad92d22cc